<section class="qualities">
  <article class="quality quality--passionate">
    <div class="quality__image">
      <img
        src="/images/qualities/qualities-passionate.svg"
        alt="Passionate quality illustration"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="quality__text">
      <h3>Passionate</h3>
      <p>
        Each project starts with an in-depth brand research to ensure we only
        create products that serve a purpose. We merge art, design, and
        technology into exciting new solutions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="quality quality--resourceful">
    <div class="quality__image">
      <img
        class="quality__image"
        src="/images/qualities/qualities-resourceful.svg"
        alt="Resourceful quality illustration"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="quality__text">
      <h3>Resourceful</h3>
      <p>
        Everything that we do has a strategic purpose. We use an agile approach
        in all of our projects and value customer collaboration. It guarantees
        superior results that fulfill our clientsâ€™ needs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="quality quality--friendly">
    <div class="quality__image">
      <img
        src="/images/qualities/qualities-friendly.svg"
        alt="Friendly quality illustration"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="quality__text">
      <h3>Friendly</h3>
      <p>
        We are a group of enthusiastic folks who know how to put people first.
        Our success depends on our customers, and we strive to give them the
        best experience a company can provide.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<style>
  .qualities {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    gap: 8rem;

    margin: 0 2.4rem;

    @media screen and (min-width: 48em) {
      margin: 0 4rem;
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 85.375em) {
      flex-direction: row;
      margin: 0 20rem;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 85.375em) {
      margin: 0 22vw;
    }
  }

  .quality {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    gap: 4.8rem;

    @media screen and (min-width: 48em) {
      flex-direction: row;
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 85.375em) {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }

  .quality--resourceful {
    & .quality__image::before {
      rotate: -45deg;
    }
  }

  .quality--friendly {
    & .quality__image::before {
      rotate: 45deg;
    }
  }

  .quality__image {
    width: 20rem;
    position: relative;

    @media screen and (min-width: 48em) {
      min-width: 20rem;
    }

    &::before {
      position: absolute;
      content: "";

      top: 0;
      left: 0;

      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;

      background-image: url("/images/bg/bg-pattern-small-circle.svg");
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: contain;

      z-index: -1;
    }
  }

  .quality__text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    gap: 1.6rem;

    text-align: center;

    @media screen and (min-width: 48em) {
      text-align: left;
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 85.375em) {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
